import React from "react";

import SiteWrapper from "./SiteWrapper.react";

function AboutHabPage() {
  return (
  	<SiteWrapper>
  		<Page.Content>
  			<Grid.Row>
       		<Grid.Col lg={3}>
					<Card isCollapsible>
				      <Card.Status color="red"/>
				      <Card.Header>
				        <Card.Title>Harmful Algal Bloom </Card.Title>
				      </Card.Header>
				      <Card.Body>
				        Subtopic 1
				        Subtopic 2
				        Subtopic 3
				      </Card.Body>
				    </Card>
				    <Card isCollapsible>
				      <Card.Status color="red"/>
				      <Card.Header>
				        <Card.Title>HAB Monitoring</Card.Title>
				      </Card.Header>
				      <Card.Body>
				        Site Locations
				        Monitoring Activites
				        Monitoring Protocol
				        Data Contribution Flow
				        Data File Format
				      </Card.Body>
				    </Card>
       		</Grid.Col>
       		<Grid.Col lg={9}>
       		
       		</Grid.Col>
       	</Grid.Row>
  		</Page.Content>
  	</SiteWrapper>
  );
}

export default AboutHabPage;
